{"tid":854392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"萬人聯署聲援！","createTime":"2018-10-09T10:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T10:56:14.000Z","uid":116054,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f5b6e08256dca277378bb229c2309eaee256f3","tid":854392,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:23:12.000Z","msg":"【封殺港獨】馬凱首發文回應 感謝香港人聯署聲援<br />\n<br />\n港府拒向香港外國記者會（FCC）第一副主席、《金融時報》亞洲新聞編輯馬凱（Victor Mallet）續發工作簽證，逾萬人聯署聲援促特區政府解釋。周一凌晨以旅客身份抵港的馬凱當時未作評論，今早8時許則首度在Facebook公開發文回應事件，他指相當感激每位參與要求政府交代拒續批簽證原因聯署的人，特別感謝香港人，指香港在過去逾七年，已是他一家人的家（I am very grateful to all those who have signed this petition, particularly those from Hong Kong, which has been home to our family for a total of more than 7 years），但文中未有談及被續申請的原因及感受等。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181009/58772899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F58772899&d=H8UCJd9e8g6in%2FebS35ortr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=989313c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F58772899&h=9fab4b6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181009/58772899</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/hong-kong-refuses-visa-to-ft-journalist-and-fcc-vp-v-mallet-authorities-please-explain?lang=en-GB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fhong-kong-refuses-visa-to-ft-journalist-and-fcc-vp-v-mallet-authorities-please-explain%3Flang%3Den-GB&d=H8UCJd9e8g6in%2FebS35ortr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2a69fa43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/hong-kong-refuses-visa-to-ft-journalist-and-fcc-vp-v-mallet-authorities-please-explain?lang=en-GB</a><br />\n 聯署簽名！<br />\n<br />\n大家可以去馬凱個帖 留言支持下佢!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/victor.mallet.56/posts/1015555